title: Sector) (Temporary Solidarity Contribution) Act 2023 (Commencement) Order
heading: 2. The 2nd day of August 2023 is appointed as the day on which the Energy
text_raw:
2. The 2nd day of August 2023 is appointed as the day on which the Energy 
(Windfall Gains in the Energy Sector) (Temporary Solidarity Contribution) Act 
2023 (No. 23 of 2023) shall come into operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

28 July, 2023. 

EAMON RYAN, 

Minister for the Environment, Climate and 
Communications. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
"Iris Oifigiúil" of 4th August, 2023.
